OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784917111
OL,3,CSpray-painted hedgehog dies as police
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues
OL,6,FA hedgehog that was discovered in a
OL,7,Fgarden in Leeds covered in spray paint
OL,8,Fhas died, despite efforts from an
OL,9,Fanimal charity.
OL,11,FThe adult female, which has been named
OL,12,FHoney, was left with breathing
OL,13,Fdifficulties after being doused with
OL,14,Fblue and yellow paint in Yeadon,
OL,15,FLeeds, earlier this month.
OL,17,FHoney was taken to Prickly Pigs
OL,18,FHedgehog Charity, in Otley, to be
OL,19,Ftreated and the team worked to clear
OL,20,Fthe paint off each individual spike.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
