SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784917111
OL,3,CSpray-painted hedgehog dies as police
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues
OL,6,FFour males, aged 44, 21, 17 and 15,
OL,7,Fwere arrested on suspicion of causing
OL,8,Funnecessary suffering to a protected
OL,9,Fanimal and have been released on bail.
OL,11,FIn an update shared on Wednesday
OL,12,Fnight, 22 July, Prickly Pigs said it
OL,13,Fwas "devastated" to announce Honey's
OL,14,Fdeath.
OL,16,FThe charity added: "It just should not
OL,17,Fhave happen full stop. It is cruel and
OL,18,Fa completely unnecessary death."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
