FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784917111
OL,3,CSpray-painted hedgehog dies as police
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues
OL,6,FVolunteers had previously said they
OL,7,Fwere hopeful Honey would make a full
OL,8,Frecovery.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV Calendar earlier this
OL,11,Fweek, Diane Cook said: "She was
OL,12,Fwheezing which we suspect was a result
OL,13,Fof potentially breathing in the fumes
OL,14,Fof the paint she's been covered in.
OL,16,F"People just unfortunately don't think
OL,17,Fwhen it comes to wildlife... this
OL,18,Fwasn't an accidental incident."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
