PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1784917111
OL,3,CSpray-painted hedgehog dies as police
OL,4,Cinvestigation continues
OL,6,FThe post announcing Honey's death has
OL,7,Freceived thousands of comments in
OL,8,Fsupport of the rescue and sharing
OL,9,Fsympathies.
OL,11,FIn the social post the rescue said it
OL,12,Fwas "an uphill battle that every
OL,13,Fwildlife rescue is the country is
OL,14,Ffacing".
OL,16,FIt added: "Hedgehogs are only on the
OL,17,Fred list because of the problems that
OL,18,Fhumans are causing".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
